    public class EffectsSettingsPane
extends AbstractSettingsPane
implements javafx.event.EventHandler<javafx.event.ActionEvent>
    Implementation of an EffectsSettingsPane as part of the tabbed side bar. This pane gathers multiple effect panes. The user can show them by choosing from a combo box.
